#: addons/Accurate_Europe_1_4.wad/addon:4 input:8 input:9 input:10 standard
msgid "Accurate Europe 1.4"
msgstr "Akkerates Europa 1.4"

#: addons/Accurate_Europe_1_4.wad/dirnames:4 input:4 standard
msgid "Add-On Maps"
msgstr "Verwiederns-Kaarten"

#: input:6 standard
msgid ""
"Warning: This map is provided as an experimental preview. Although it is "
"better in many ways than Europa 1.2 that it replaces, it probably still has "
"bugs. Furthermore, it is a very large map with more player positions than "
"generally recommended, so it has high hardware requirements.  —   A map for "
"roleplaying historical empires.  – This map of Europe aims to be as accurate "
"as practically possible in Widelands.  – EASY: Ottoman Empire, Sweden, "
"Russian Empire, Carthage  – MEDIUM: French Empire, British Empire, Spain, "
"German Empire, Roman Empire  – HARD: Egypt, Poland, Greece <br> "
"<br>----------------------- <br>v1.4 somes minor fix with ports"
msgstr ""
"Wahrschau: Deese Kaart word as noch nich steviger Utkiek klaargeven. Dat is "
"in mennig Aarden beter as Europa 1.2, wat ’t utwesselt, enthollt man aver "
"wull noch Fehlers. Daarto is dat eene bannig grote Kaart mit mehr Spelers, "
"as normaal anraden worden, stellt also hooge Anförderns an de Reekner. – "
"Eene Kaart, um histoorisk Rieken natospölen. – Deese Kaart vun Europa "
"versöcht, so akkeraat as in Widelands praktisk mögelk to wesen. – LICHT: "
"Ottomaansk Riek, Sweden, Russisk Riek, Kartago – MIDDEL: Frankriek, Engelks "
"Riek, Spaanje, Düütsches Riek, Römisk Riek – STUUV: Ägypten, Polen, "
"Grekenland <br> <br> ----------------------- <br>v1.4 eenige lütte Ofhelpens "
"mit Muden"

#: input:7 input:14 standard
msgid ""
"The wide rivers are navigable to create a ”trade network”.  All players have "
"their own challenges, but are relatively balanced to be playable:  – British "
"Empire: create sustainable colonies  – Russian Empire: Very large distances …"
msgstr ""
"Up de wieden Stromen is Seefahrt mögelk, um een »Hannelsnett« uptobauen. All "
"Spelers hebben hör eegen Rutfödderungen, sünd aver eenigermaten utgleken, um "
"spöölbaar to wesen: – Engelsk Riek: sett versörgbaare Kolonien up – Russisk "
"Riek: bannig grote Feernten …"
